; rec_deep_nontco_250k.esk - NON-tail recursion asserted AT the empirically
; documented safe depth.
;
; Empirical limits (2026-07-02, macOS arm64 M2 Ultra, default stacks):
;   JIT -r : depth 260000 PASS, 270000 SIGILL (rc 132, NO diagnostic)
;   AOT    : depth 260000 PASS, 280000 SIGILL
; First failing depth: 270000 (JIT) / <=280000 (AOT). The runtime guard
; ESHKOL_MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH=100000 (lib/core/runtime_list_helpers.cpp) does
; NOT cover this plain user-code recursion; the crash is a raw stack blowout.
; See found/deep_recursion_270k_no_diagnostic.esk.
;
; 250000 gives margin under the first failure while staying 2.5x above the
; 10^5 target depth.
(define (down n)
  (if (= n 0) 0 (+ 1 (down (- n 1)))))
(display "OK ") (display (down 250000)) (newline)
